          <div class="dd-equipment-specs">
            <div class="dd-spec"><span>WORKING AREA</span><strong>1300 x 2500 mm / 2100 x 2800 mm</strong></div>
            <div class="dd-spec"><span>TOOL CHANGER</span><strong>8/12 Slots Linear ATC</strong></div>
