        <div class="dd-quote-unit">
          <span class="dd-quote-large">“</span>
          <p>We saw machine which another customer bought in your company... Is it exactly this machine?</p>
          <div style="font-size: 8px; opacity: 0.4; margin-top: 10px; letter-spacing: 2px;">2023: FIRST CONTACT</div>
        </div>
        <div class="dd-quote-unit">
          <span class="dd-quote-large">“</span>
          <p>We want the size of the work table to be 2.10*2.80 so that we can put a countertop tile.</p>
          <div style="font-size: 8px; opacity: 0.4; margin-top: 10px; letter-spacing: 2px;">2026: CAPACITY EXPANSION</div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- SECTION 09: FINAL CTA -->
